  <brief_title>Ivabradine Versus Propranolol for Induced Hypotension in Endoscopic Sinus Surgery</brief_title>
  <official_title>Comparative Study Between Oral Ivabradine Versus Oral Propranolol for Induced Hypotension in Functional Endoscopic Sinus Surgery</official_title>
