  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      the study is designed to compare the effect of addition of oral Ivabradine, propranolol to&#xD;
      general anesthesia aimed reduction in blood loss during functional endoscopic sinus surgery.&#xD;
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
